title: Beautiful 1bed apartment  $2700
posting_body: ['This contemporary 1 bedroom and 1 bath apartment is inside a Fourplex property.', 'All properties are fully furnished and all-inclusive.', 'Cozy with all the basic necessities for a pleasant stay.', 'This unit is good for couples, solo adventures, and business travelers.', 'Very good location, centrally located 1 block from Coral Gables.', 'Near to everything in Miami.', 'It will take you little time to get anywhere, restaurants, markets, shopping, nightlife, attractions, airport, beaches…', 'Distances:', 'Brickell & Downtown -> 5 miles', 'Coconut Grove -> 1.5 miles', 'Coral Gables -> 1/2 mile to Miracle Mile and everything Coral Gables has to offer.', 'Restaurants, Shops at Merrick Park, Miracle Mile, and shopping are all just blocks away!', 'Miami International airport-> 5 miles', 'Cruise Port -> 5 miles from the cruise port', 'Metrorail Station-> (15 min walk)', 'Minutes away from US1 which connects to all major highways', '1/2 mile to Miracle Mile and everything Coral Gables has to offer.', 'LEASE TERMS (SHORT & LONG TERM RENTAL AVAILABLE)', 'Rent includes the electricity, cable, wireless high-speed internet, water, sewer, trash removal, and pest control', 'Security Deposit required']
